thread.title: Carole

author: Carole
title: Carole
text: Would recommend company and what a great way to discover all kinds of 'new' meats. Postage, packing, excellent. Ordered lots, so haven't had a chance to eat it all yet! However, have now eaten a couple of the 'ready meals' which were sublime & well portioned.. On the meals that have been home cooked, meat has been tender and tasty! Now going back for the REALLY exotic. Finally, for anyone who needs to find 'A healthier way' ~ look no further ~ these meats are a darn sight healthier than anything you can get in Supermarkets and most butchers.
